T1  - Capital Structure and Corporate Control: The Effect of Antitakeover Statutes on Firm Leverage
AU  - Garvey, Gerald T.
AU  - Hanka, Gordon
Y1  - 1999/04/01
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/04/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/0022-1082.00116
T2  - The Journal of Finance
